Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.93,0:44:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那一把槍  沒有士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.20,0:44:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一個人都沒有  -塞申斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.90,0:44:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.93,0:44:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這工廠有自己的信號塔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.93,0:45:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發出很強的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.00,0:45:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.66,0:45:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32公里內的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.60,0:45:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能聽見我們和基地的通話
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.06,0:45:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何叛軍的電臺都能截獲我們的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.76,0:45:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最不用擔心的就是叛軍
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.76,0:45:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡快和奧倫德將軍取得聯系
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.70,0:45:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.50,0:45:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.96,0:45:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.20,0:45:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.90,0:45:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.50,0:45:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.70,0:45:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是我們的新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.16,0:45:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  你們能幫上大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.20,0:46:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  小鐵漢  看看你有什么本事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.93,0:46:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得問你些事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的屏障  是你的主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.70,0:46:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們父親  他們父親知道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.70,0:46:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們父親沿著建筑外圍
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.40,0:46:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒了幾桶鐵屑
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.23,0:46:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了他們的命
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.96,0:46:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.96,0:46:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個小拳擊手是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.23,0:46:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計  你沒事吧  繼續  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.20,0:46:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.86,0:47:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是鬼魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.06,0:47:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.13,0:47:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說別說那個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.21,0:47:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問他那些東西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.16,0:47:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.06,0:47:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.30,0:47:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在生與死之間
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.66,0:47:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法安息
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.13,0:47:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.83,0:47:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是因為戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.96,0:47:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他們的父親撒下了那些鐵屑
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.00,0:47:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他比我們任何人都更了解那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.23,0:47:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問她父親在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.30,0:48:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她弟弟波格丹還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.00,0:48:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以為父親只是出去求助了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.90,0:48:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在外面弄屏障的時候死的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.16,0:48:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只能把他帶回這里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.66,0:48:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.80,0:48:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以嗎  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.86,0:48:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陶瓷片
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.36,0:48:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問她父親是怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.69,0:48:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵屑能阻擋幽魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.63,0:48:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.60,0:49:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.90,0:49:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬薩羅維
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.00,0:49:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-馬薩羅維是什么  -是一個地名
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.96,0:49:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上游的一個區域
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.10,0:49:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這一切的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.23,0:49:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂殺人就是從那里開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.26,0:49:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.20,0:49:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說就把直升機停這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.20,0:49:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從這個屋頂撤離  趕緊離開這里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.00,0:49:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里到處都是電話線和電力線
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.20,0:49:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升機得飛得又低又慢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.83,0:49:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小孩都能扛著火箭筒把它打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.63,0:49:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校  現在是什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.75,0:49:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和基地聯系過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.83,0:49:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯系過了  將軍會派直升機來接我們
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.75,0:49:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及坦克來確保降落廣場周邊安全
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.60,0:49:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距這里約八百米  黎明到達
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.70,0:49:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行的話會很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.20,0:49:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我們能帶著小孩撐過八百米嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.96,0:49:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.34,0:49:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的路要么被封死要么埋了地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.33,0:49:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們用信號塔和基地聯系了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.60,0:49:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都知道我們的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.84,0:50:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得盡快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.93,0:50:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西還在街上亂晃
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.92,0:50:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在這種情況下出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.23,0:50:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒有任何看到和對付它們的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.20,0:50:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比等著它們闖進來要好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.40,0:50:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒死的唯一原因就是外面的那道屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.60,0:50:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們遲早會進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.91,0:50:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.30,0:50:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-先消停一下  -我們得冒險一試
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.83,0:50:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是目前最好的計劃  -少校
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.73,0:50:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說我能增加成功到達廣場的幾率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.66,0:50:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你說  -看看周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.73,0:50:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里到處都是這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.73,0:50:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵屑
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.26,0:50:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵能阻止那些超光譜異形
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.66,0:50:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  把它做成武器
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.20,0:50:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-臟彈  -這是今晚最好的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.13,0:50:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集手榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.20,0:51:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.76,0:51:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面我需要你做我們的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.60,0:51:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帶著攝像機走路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.52,0:51:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有更好的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.63,0:51:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個攝像機本身就能投射相符波長的紫外線
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.33,0:51:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能將它內部翻轉過來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.71,0:51:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過改變一些結構的極性
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.73,0:51:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也許能把攝像機改造成探照燈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.06,0:51:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們憑肉眼就能看見它們
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.80,0:51:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能大大改善我們的境況
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.25,0:51:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能和基地的車隊通話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.90,0:51:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許能告訴它們
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.08,0:51:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何對裝備做同樣的調整
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.33,0:51:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們過來時也需要能看見它們的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.30,0:51:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你聯系基地的主工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.13,0:52:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.03,0:52:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會在車上裝備任何你需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.16,0:52:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將需求列表復述一遍給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.86,0:52:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.60,0:52:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你需要的是一個
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.82,0:52:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發射短波長光的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.03,0:52:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會詳細告訴你怎么改線
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.96,0:52:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以裝在坦克上的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.90,0:53:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巷那頭有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.00,0:53:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計們  有動靜  能看看是什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.36,0:53:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.13,0:53:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車隊那邊怎么說
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.62,0:53:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次通訊在50分鐘以前
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.86,0:53:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在前往撤離點的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.23,0:54:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們來了  拿好你們的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.00,0:54:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們15秒后離開這里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.23,0:54:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.26,0:54:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是去撤離點最快的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.57,0:54:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說可以帶我們走另一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.33,0:54:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔爾博特  你和克萊恩一起
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.91,0:54:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞茲  你領頭
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.76,0:54:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.83,0:54:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.00,0:54:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.36,0:54:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.80,0:54:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.03,0:54:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都在
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.60,0:54:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看起來沒問題  -我們走  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.73,0:54:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  她說這里右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.30,0:55:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意  六點鐘方向
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.06,0:55:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快走  -快走
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.66,0:55:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.16,0:55:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.36,0:55:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.83,0:55:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.66,0:55:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.26,0:55:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.20,0:55:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  路易斯  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.95,0:55:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.73,0:55:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-進來  -這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.06,0:55:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.20,0:56:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.73,0:56:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.06,0:56:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快跟上  -跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.70,0:56:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-扶他起來  -起來
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.30,0:56:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒事  -走  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.23,0:56:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍拿穩
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.66,0:56:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-趴下  -找掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.66,0:56:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  博士  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.03,0:56:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.70,0:56:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人陣亡  一人陣亡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.10,0:57:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.13,0:57:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快跑  -那邊有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.66,0:57:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.63,0:57:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說"就在前面  拱門下方"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.36,0:57:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.30,0:57:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-慢著  -她說就是這里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.03,0:57:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  走
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.23,0:57:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該安全
