Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.80,1:27:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波色-愛因斯坦凝聚態
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.03,1:28:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那些X光線
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.00,1:28:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在掃描人類  而且是分子級別的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.96,1:28:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后用凝聚態打印出來
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.90,1:28:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是條裝配線
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.10,1:28:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像某種...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.26,1:28:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工業生產線
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.76,1:28:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.80,1:28:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是個武器
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.10,1:29:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里發生了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.33,1:29:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是出現了災難性故障
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.90,1:29:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半單元格破損而且已經空了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.80,1:29:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是結構損壞讓它們逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.13,1:29:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了潘多拉魔盒
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.73,1:29:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.80,1:29:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人出現
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.20,1:29:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12點鐘方向
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.90,1:30:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-開槍  -它起來了  它們又聚合了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.00,1:30:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要來了  -瞄準目標
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.06,1:30:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有一個重新聚合了  -干掉它
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.96,1:30:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央政府高端研究顧問
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.36,1:30:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要阻止這個局面的  確實是失控了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.23,1:30:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能翻譯這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.20,1:30:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是緊急關閉程序
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.01,1:30:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面一半的字我都沒見過
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.70,1:30:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一半寫的什么
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.73,1:31:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解耦  解耦程序
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.06,1:31:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷開臍帶鏈接
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.22,1:31:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以中斷神經活動
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.26,1:31:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -所以你得解鎖所有端口
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.03,1:31:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后拉這個
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.12,1:31:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱桿  斷開所有電纜
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.90,1:31:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.76,1:31:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就能阻止它們了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.26,1:31:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.60,1:32:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  給我起來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.76,1:32:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  又增加了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.73,1:32:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現一個
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.16,1:33:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.76,1:33:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-克萊恩  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.63,1:33:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.13,1:33:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都斷開了  沒有用啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.73,1:34:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩  拉操縱桿  中間那個
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.13,1:34:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -不
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.73,1:35:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-結束了嗎  -不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.26,1:36:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還能走路嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.16,1:36:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒事  -來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.23,1:36:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得找條出路
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.70,1:36:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-聽到了嗎  -聽到了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.00,1:36:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這里了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.70,1:37:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不只是掃描人類
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.83,1:37:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們也不僅僅是打印物
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.30,1:37:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是控制他們的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.93,1:37:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是真正的尸體
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.36,1:37:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個都是一條生命
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.66,1:37:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.83,1:37:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非活著
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.96,1:37:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也沒有死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.70,1:37:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被困在了生死之間
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.36,1:37:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是十分痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.20,1:37:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.26,1:37:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.80,1:37:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎么知道他們能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.83,1:37:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法證明
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.70,1:37:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.83,1:37:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許科學確實無法回答一切問題
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.63,1:38:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.06,1:38:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.70,1:38:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們來這里的目的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.16,1:38:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是證據  是你來的目的  記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.03,1:38:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎  已經死了那么多人  你說的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.90,1:38:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你說你要知道原因  -已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.96,1:38:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得為大局考慮
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.90,1:38:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為大局
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.23,1:39:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫他們依次下機
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.86,1:39:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后續還有更多傷員
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.93,1:39:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送他們去第五小隊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.16,1:39:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這邊這邊  -小心他的脖子
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.36,1:39:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.63,1:39:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手給我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.13,1:39:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.96,1:39:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.30,1:40:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.63,1:40:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了新調查隊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.06,1:40:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要把馬薩羅維拆成碎片
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.70,1:40:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測量一切
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.26,1:40:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試圖重新建造
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.83,1:40:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪所有權
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.26,1:40:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要我問你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.68,1:40:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿不愿意參加  我答應了  但是
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.83,1:40:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來的目的已經達到了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.13,1:41:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真是永不停息啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.63,1:41:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恐怕他們是不會
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.90,1:41:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說了你可以直接拎包回弗吉尼亞
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.20,1:41:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角洲小隊  出發
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.80,1:41:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
